<h1>Fuzzy Logic</h1>
<p>BlitzMax translation of Mat Bucklands' C++ Fuzzy Logic implementation described in the book <a href="http://www.ai-junkie.com/books/toc_pgaibe.html">Programming Game AI by Example</a>.</p>

<h2>What use is it?</h2>
<p>With <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fuzzy_logic">Fuzzy Logic</a> it's possible to let your game agents make decisions like humans do. A nice tutorial/explanation can be found at the <a href="http://www.byond.com/members/DreamMakers?command=view_post&post=37966">Dream Makers</a> website.</p>

